  ('Life Science and Technology (BSc)', NULL, 'English-taught joint degree between Leiden University and Delft University of Technology; covers molecular biology, chemistry, and biotechnology with engineering applications; strong sciences background required (Biology, Chemistry, Mathematics at A-level equivalent); diploma equivalent to Dutch VWO; IELTS 6.5 overall minimum 6.0 per component; regular deadline 15 March; non-EEA deadline 1 May; physics or mathematics desirable; Leiden ranks QS Top 100 World (Biological Sciences)', NULL, 6.5, 90, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ABB', 32, NULL, NULL, 58)
